Package org.ivoa.dm.stc.trans

Class PermuteAxis

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.stc.trans.PermuteAxis
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
@Entity @VoDml(id="trans:PermuteAxis", role=objectType) public class PermuteAxis extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
Entry for the Permute operation, this object defines the mapping of input dimension to output dimension. The output dimension is determined from its order in the axismap list. objectType: PermuteAxis
